      • getLine

        public static TagLine getLine(TagController controller,
                              org.bukkit.entity.Player p,
                              int lineIndex)
        Gets a line by the specified index. Line numbers go from top to bottom, starting at zero and not including the player's nametag. The line must exist in order to be retrieved.
        Parameters:
        controller - The controller to get a line for
        p - The player to get a line of
        lineIndex - The index of the line to get, starting at zero at the top and goes to the bottom
        Returns:
        The line object that allows editing of the line

      • updateLocs

        public static void updateLocs(org.bukkit.entity.Player p)
        Update the locations of the entities that correspond to a player. They are always at y=-10 below the player. This is used in onMove, onTeleport, and onWorldChange to ensure the entities are still loaded by all clients who can see the player they correspond to.
        Parameters:
        p - The player whose locations should be updated
